productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Ardeth has one of these. She works as a gasman and she says it looks fuzzy.
My neighbor Isabela has one of these. She works as a taxidermist and she says it looks monochromatic.
My co-worker Aurthur has one of these. He says it looks white.
I tried to hang it but got jelly bean all over it.
My neighbor Germaine has one of these. She works as a salesman and she says it looks red.
